  ('dietitian-moex-00360', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-ad4b6c8a', 'sub-dietitian-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關蛋類特性與烹調製備的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["蛋黃醬是利用蛋黃中的卵磷脂作為乳化劑製作之成品", "蒸蛋時應將蛋液打發並以大火蒸，才能確保成品無孔洞且質地柔軟", "雞蛋若要冷凍保存，應該要以完整帶殼的型態較佳", "製作天使蛋糕應將蛋白攪打至乾性發泡期，使泡沫體積較大且穩定"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:50+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "60192659f8f1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "07e12825c8a5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "102", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "團體膳食設計與管理", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00361', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-ad4b6c8a', 'sub-dietitian-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '漁獲物撈起後應即刻進行保鮮三C，有關三C之原則，下列何者正確？', '["冷凍、包裝、販賣", "清潔、冷卻、包裝", "分割、清潔、冷凍", "冷卻、冷凍、分割"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:50+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "60192659f8f1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "07e12825c8a5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "102", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "團體膳食設計與管理", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
